Usage: fillNotch [-help] [-area {x1 y1 x2 y2}] [-useExistingDrcResult]
                 [-useNonDefaultSpacing] [-report <string> ]

-help                        # Prints out the command usage
-area {x1 y1 x2 y2}          # specifies the area to check (box, optional)
-report <string>             # Specifies the report file that contains the
                             # violations informations (string, optional)
-useExistingDrcResult        # Help to check the VG marker convexCornerSpacing
                             # (bool, optional)
-useNonDefaultSpacing        # If a net has a nondefault rule, checks the
                             # nondefault rule spacing values for every route
                             # of the net (bool, optional)